          "reviewBody": "Google map location is accurate. You can reach here by taking howrah maidan small buses and get down near howrah maidan triangular park and follow the google map. It will take around 10 min from howrah station to reach here. It is a small school conducting online exams and having streams like science,arts and commerce.",
