            "ratingValue": "3",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Date of Examination: 11 June 2023.\nServer connection for conducting examination is quite bad as of now & air conditioning machines are not capable of cooling down (atmospheric temperature 38°c & high humidity) the lab room; staffs are decent and helpful though.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Marias Day School - Howrah Railway Station,Kadam Tala"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Ritvik Seth"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-03-09",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "If you are planning to take admission in this institute please stop right there. There are several reasons for this...\n1. In IX there is an option between maths and EVS.. many students opt for EVS but we know maths is highly important for any career.. and we cannot expect from 13 year old to choose between maths and EVS because most likely they will opt for easier option.\n2. In XI students from commerce are made to choose between business studies and maths but we should know that both are extremely important for further opportunities in commerce.\n3. Violence - recently a local news channel also covered this news about violence in our school.. many highschool boys after exam came out on streets and started beating other boys with bats and thick wooden sticks..\nNot only this many highschool boys during recess had damaged school property like fans , table, beanch, glass windows etc..",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
